Privacy Policy 

At Simple Game, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of personal information we collect and how we use it.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information from our users. Our game does not require any registration or login, and we do not ask for any personal information such as name, email address, or phone number.

We may collect non-personal information such as device type, operating system, and game usage data to improve our game and provide a better user experience. This information is collected anonymously and cannot be used to identify individual users.

Third-Party Services

Our game may use third-party services such as advertising networks or analytics providers. These services may collect non-personal information about your device and usage of our game to provide targeted ads or analytics insights. We do not control the data collection practices of these third-party services and encourage you to review their privacy policies.

Children's Privacy

Our game is intended for general audiences and does not target children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years old.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time without prior notice. Your continued use of our game after any changes to this policy will constitute your acceptance of the updated policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at fdessalew@gmail.com
